      "Food provision meets the whole standard: nutritionally adequate across the day (not just at main meals), sufficient in quantity with more available, varied across the menu cycle, culturally competent, attractive on the plate, and served at safe and pleasant temperatures — adequacy is the floor, enjoyment is the target",
